<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="colour-v">colo(u)r <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kʌlə(r)/    美 /'kʌlər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>给...着色：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>colour one’s hair
染发</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They coloured the wall white.
他们把墙刷白了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>变色；脸红</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>colo(u)red /'kʌləd/ adj <br />
colo(u)rless /'kʌlələs/ adj   </p></div>